    "def job_split(row):\n",
    "    job,dname=row['job'],row['dname']\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if dname in job and ',' in job:\n",
    "        return job.split(',')[0].strip()\n",
    "    \n",
    "    if job.startswith(dname):\n",
    "        return job.split(' ')[-1].strip()\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return job\n",
    "\n",
    "df['job']=df.apply(job_split,axis=1)\n"
   ]
